div.div:
Nearly a century after magic was recognized as a real form of technology, Miyuki Shiba begins her term at Magic High School. An “honor” student, she dreamed of enjoying school with her older brother Tatsuya, an “irregular” student. But a rift between the gifted Course 1 students and the inferior Course 2 students could stand in the way. This time, Miyuki is the star of the show!
(Source: Funimation)

I, the protagonist, was just an ordinary high school girl, but suddenly I was reincarnated as a spider monster in a fantasy world. Not only that, but I awakened in a dungeon filled with vicious monsters. Armed with only my human knowledge and my overwhelming positivity, I'm forced to use spiderwebs and traps to defeat far stronger monsters just to stay alive... So begins the labyrinth survival story of a girl with incredible mental strength living as one of the lowest-ranked beasts!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

A scatterbrained, talentless civil servant returned as the heavenly Demon. He now wished to live the rest of his life peacefully, as his days in the Murim world were full of conflict and bloodshed. However... "Please be my father until I graduate." He suddenly gained a daughter out of nowhere.
Akuyaku Reijou wa Kiraware Kizoku ni Koi wo Suru

Aikawa Eri dies in a traffic accident after staying up all night playing an otome game. She reincarnates as Eris, the villainess of her favorite game. In order to avoid the bad end, she tries her best to change the story, but as expected, it’s hard to rewrite fate…
She is abandoned by the prince. Even more, her life almost ends when she is attacked by a gang of thugs, but a young man appears...
Will the antisocial prince change her destiny? This is the reincarnated villainess’s rebirth romance fantasy!

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
